Alessandro Nesta agreed to a contract with the Montreal Impact
of  Major League Soccer .  Nesta, who won the  World Cup  with Italy in 2006, spent the
past 10 seasons at Milan, helping the club win the Champions
League in 2003 and 2007 and two Serie A titles. Heâ€™ll join
